You'll need to install NLTK:

pip3 install nltk

also, you'll need to install the associated WordNet files:

http://www.nltk.org/howto/wordnet.html

python3 wnlookup.py < TGTM.glosses.csv > results.csv


output is 3 columns:

* frequency
* gloss
* merged list of WN synonyms

http://www.nltk.org/howto/wordnet.html

